      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**AEGIS Forecast Drift — Performance** · Governed read-only **V2** snapshot via datasource `aegis-forecast-drift-csv`. Accuracy / error-based drift between forecast versions (`performance_drift_score`, governed family weight **20%**). A signal is **computable** when it has a non-empty `performance_drift_score`; **coverage** is the computable share of the filtered universe. KPIs, the details table and run panels honor all five shared filters (Forecast Key · Forecast Version · Region · Drift Status · Run ID); the drift trend intentionally ignores Forecast Version; the Non-computable Summary honors only Forecast Key and Forecast Version."
      }
    },
